flowRoot.flowPara: CHAPTER 3. THE PROVENANCE ~35min

Good news! I've got a buyer lined up. Here's the problem. He's a little squeamish about this particular collection. Says he needs documented proof that these are authentic. Now, unless one of you is forger, we're gonna need to acquire those provenance records from deep within the Gallery archives. Security is a little heavier down there - watch out for those pressure sensors. As for our money - don't worry - I'll front us the team loot we've earned so far for this next job. Looks like the archives also have some jewels awaiting appraisals. So, your objective is to get both documents, and for every jewel you bring back I'll add $3k to team loot.

UPON SUCCESS: Excellent! I think this will be a good relationship. Here's $6k for team loot (plus payout for extra jewels). At this point I'll let you promote any non-Busted characters for $3k each and $2k for each Skill.
Huh. That's funny. These records have some authentication facts about these paintings. They don't match. We stole some fakes!! Ok let me do some digging and figure what happened.
As a team you have 🔍🔍🔍 and 💡💡 to use in planning. (Team loot $0k.)
SUGGESTED CHARACTERS and SKILLS
RED: Angry Locksmith with Hurry and Smash 'n' Grab
GREEN: Thug with Yank Wires and Bypass
BLUE: Burglar with Wing It and Hit 'n' Run
YELLOW: Script Kiddie with Hit 'n' Run and Hurry (4-players only)
CHAPTER 4. THE COLLECTOR ~35min

Turns out there's a bigger fan of these paintings than me! I have no idea who he hired for the job, but he beat us to it. This collector doesn't show up on the provenance, so he clearly didn't acquire these legally. How selfish! This artwork needs to circulate. Let's liberate his collection. Plus, we might as well put these fakes to good use. Your objective is to swap in the fruit painting fakes and steal the authentic ones. Choose carefully who carries in the fake paintings. And feel free to take as much money from this cheese-eating art hoarder as you can.
UPON SUCCESS: Look at you professionals! Here's another $6k for your time. Go ahead and promote any non-Busted Characters for $3k each and $2k for each Skill.
CHAPTER 5. THE EMBASSY ~35min

Hey remember that Collector? Well, turns out he's the paranoid type. He knew something went awry last night and used his connections to find me. That's the downside of knowing everyone... everyone knows you. Anyway, I'm being held here at the Italian embassy awaiting extradition. If you all would be so kind and let me out, I would be happy to pay your for your time. Your objective is to have me escape. There also seems to be some nice jewels around here - I can sell them for $3k each if you happen to grab any along the way.
UPON SUCCESS: Thank you! Now let's finish what we started. Here's another $8k for the team loot. Again, for anyone who isn't Busted go ahead promote them for $3k or upgrade Skills for $2k each.
CHAPTER 6. THE REDEMPTION JOB ~35min

I've been studying these documents. As it turns out, they belong to the ancestors of the Gallery's curator. He won't let these go. I figure if I turn them in this curator will still pursue extradition on me. If we can return the rightful paintings without a trace we can all call it even. Your objective is to swap in at least three real paintings in for their originals. Sadly, as you would expect, The Gallery has tightened up their security quite a bit given this recent streak of heists. But I'm confident you're up to the task.
After this, I need to lay low for a while. You should find another source for jobs until I come and find you. Best of luck!
CHAPTER 5. THE LONG SWAP ~40min

Ok I got this great tip on a huge job. I know this hobbyist art forger who works for the upcoming exhibition. He's been working on the Grapes of Venice painting between shifts. He finished his masterpiece. All we have to do is the switch. He got the piece as close as he could... which is to say not very close. We need to take the fake painting and swap it with the original. As soon as you reach the real painting, I'll detonate some C4 on a nearby wall and you can all escape.
*When someone reaches the asterisk token, create an exit on this hex and initiate escape phase immediately. This may also be done during the Escape phase.
UPON SUCCESS: Fantastic! Here's another $8k for your time. Go ahead and promote any non-Busted Characters for $3k each and $2k for each Skill.
CH 5. STANDALONE CHALLENGE:
To try Ch. 5 directly without doing the entire campaign, use these conditions:
Team cash: $6k (no team loot)
Safecracker + Ninja + Steal
Operative + Splice In + Extract
Grease Man + Concoct + Assault
Black Hat + Prowl + Blast
